Project Overview:
Rotikaya Media Sdn. Bhd. Sales Tracking and Management System is a Laravel-based web application for managing sales records, invoices, payments, reminders, reporting, and role-based operations for three core roles (admin, accountant, sales staff). The system replaces spreadsheet/manual workflows with centralized records, dashboard visibility, automated overdue reminders, and auditable financial operations. All implementation and future changes must stay aligned with the documented requirements and acceptance criteria.

